00:17:11,100 --> 00:17:15,440
 What it's saying here is this is Shalom, not Sabbath.

304
00:17:15,440 --> 00:17:18,980
 This is God standing back and saying, "This is just as it was created to be.

305
00:17:18,980 --> 00:17:20,760
 Everything is where it should be.

306
00:17:20,760 --> 00:17:22,500
 This is a place of peace.

307
00:17:22,500 --> 00:17:23,860
 This is rest."

308
00:17:23,860 --> 00:17:26,540
 Are you with me?

