00:17:26,540 --> 00:17:30,460
 So when Jesus says, "Come to me, all you who are wearing burdens, and I will give you rest,"

310
00:17:30,460 --> 00:17:34,300
 he's not speaking about Sabbath.

311
00:17:34,300 --> 00:17:35,580
 Come on, church.

